column5: Will be leaving July 18 from central Wi. about 5 PM and going to Ear Falls. Any supermarkets open 24 hours around Virginia? Want some perishables like milk and eggs.
The Virginia SuperOne is open 6am-Midnight. The International Falls SuperOne says it's open 24 hrs. Do a web search on "Internatilnal Falls Grocery Stores". Give them a call to verify.

If you're refering to the grocery store that shares the parking lot with Barney's restaurant in International Falls, I can tell you that they're open at 4 in the morning. The fresh bakery isn't done yet and its cruel to have to wait. But its worth it.
